Company Overview

ELIZABETH ARDEN INTERNATIONAL HOLDING INC is in the Offices of Holding Companies, N.E.C. industry in Miramar, FL.  This company currently has approximately 20 to 50 employees  and  annual sales of Over $1,000,000,000.













Company Details

Location Type:
						Branch
					

Industry:
						Offices of Holding Companies, N.E.C.
					

Ownership: Private
						
					

Year Founded:
						1993
					

Sales Range:
						Over $1,000,000,000
					

Employees:
						20 to 50


     
    
   
  

