            Business Description
        



Elizabeth Arden International Holding is located in Miramar, Florida. This organization primarily operates in the Perfumes, Cosmetics and other Toilet Preparations business / industry within the Chemicals and Allied Products sector. This organization has been operating for approximately 17 years. Elizabeth Arden International Holding is estimated to generate $8.4 million in annual revenues, and employs approximately 5 people at this headquarters location.









